the "I see dead people" jokes.

04:16.933 --> 04:18.170
Yeah, that never gets old.

04:18.257 --> 04:19.351
- I bet.
- Yeah.

04:19.735 --> 04:20.815
All right.

04:20.904 --> 04:22.688
- You know, when... Sit down.
- Yeah.

